OL,6,FThe move caused disquiet because his
OL,7,Ffirst spell, between 2012 and 2015,
OL,8,Fcoincided in part with the racism
OL,9,Fscandal that has enveloped the White
OL,10,FRose in recent times.
OL,12,FThe 76-year-old businessman, formerly
OL,13,Fchair of the ECB, has apologised to
OL,14,Fthose who suffered discrimination at
OL,15,Fthe county ` after previous comments
OL,16,Fthat some of the abuse represented
OL,17,F"banter" ` and appeared in front of
OL,18,Fthe CMS committee in February.
