OL,6,FCommittee chair Caroline Dinenage
OL,7,Fsaid: "The start of the county cricket
OL,8,Fseason is always a time for optimism,
OL,9,Fand we hope that members at Headingley
OL,10,Fcan look forward to a successful
OL,11,Ffuture, with a board committed to a
OL,12,Fmember-led club and a continued focus
OL,13,Fon tackling discrimination.
OL,15,F"The ECB should keep a close eye on
OL,16,Fprogress to ensure Yorkshire continues
OL,17,Fgoing down the road to reform."
