OL,6,FThe committee also shone a light on
OL,7,Fthe governing body and its wider
OL,8,Fresponsibilities to the game,
OL,9,Fincluding matters of class and gender-
OL,10,Fbased equality.
OL,12,FThe report noted: "We are concerned
OL,13,Fthat their ambition may not translate
OL,14,Finto action on some of the ICEC's most
OL,15,Fpowerful recommendations. If this
OL,16,Fhappens the ECB's aim to be the most
OL,17,Finclusive sport in England and Wales
OL,18,Fmay not be reached.
